defaultMeasuring business crime default2.4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultA fundamental problem with assessing the impact of business crime 
defaulti
defaults that there is no agreed definition of it
default.  
defaultWe cannot fight 
defaultit 
defaulteffectively until the true scale of the problem is measured and understood.   
defaultThis is why the BRC fully supports the work by DCC Sue Fish, ACPO lead for Business Crime, to introduce a single, national 
defaultbusiness crime 
defaultdefinition.
default  
defaultThis, along with the capability of police forces to ‘tag’ such crime on their recording systems, would represent a major step forward. It 
defaultwould 
defaultallow 
defaultthere to be 
defaultfocused partnership
defaults
default between businesses and the police to tackle retail crime, utilising resources more effectively to target hot spots within each force area.
